t = Template(
    """
        <%def name="foo()">
            hi im foo ${caller.body(y=5)}
        </%def>

        <%call expr="foo()" args="y, **kwargs">
            this is the body, y is ${y}
        </%call>
"""
    )
assert result_lines(t.render()) == ['hi im foo', 'this is the body, y is 5']
